column7: An outdoor photograph \ taken of one of the entrances of the Alton Mill Arts Centre. The building is made of stone and has an arched doorway accompanied by various windows. The sky is blue and sprinkled with fluffy white clouds.
An outdoor photograph taken of the backside of the Alton Mill.

An outdoor photograph of the waterway on the rear side of the mill. There is a wooden bridge supported by large stone foundation extending across a man-made waterfall. In the background, the mill is visible with a green tree extending into frame from the right side.
